    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0786b16"/><head><date from-iso="+0907-06-10" key="j20524952058534" to-iso="+0923-12-22">梁</date>撫州曹山<persName key="A009449">本寂</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0786b17"/><persName key="A009449">釋本寂</persName>，姓黃氏，<placeName key="PL000000018518">泉州蒲田</placeName>人也。其邑唐季多<lb
ed="T" n="0786b18"/>衣冠士子僑寓，儒風振起，號小稷下焉。<persName key="A009449">寂</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0786b19"/>少染魯風，率多強學，自爾淳粹獨凝，道性<lb
ed="T" n="0786b20"/>天發。<date key="j20344392034803" from-iso="+0858-01-01" to-iso="+0858-12-31">年惟十九</date>，二親始聽出家。入福州<placeName key="PL000000017137">雲名<lb
ed="T" n="0786b21"/>山</placeName>。<date key="j20366302036995" from-iso="+0864-01-01" to-iso="+0864-12-31">年二十五</date>，登于戒足，凡諸舉措，若老苾<lb
ed="T" n="0786b22"/>芻。<date notBefore-iso="+0860-12-21" key="j20355242036679" notAfter-iso="+0864-02-19">咸通之初</date>，禪宗興盛，風起於<persName key="A001984">大溈</persName>也。至<lb
ed="T" n="0786b23"/>如<persName key="A010291">石頭</persName>、<persName key="A010510">藥山</persName>其名寢頓，會<persName key="A009489">洞山</persName>憫物，高其<lb
ed="T" n="0786b24"/><persName key="A010291">石頭</persName>，往來請益，學同洙泗。<persName key="A009449">寂</persName>處眾如愚，發<lb
ed="T" n="0786b25"/>言若訥。後被請住臨川<placeName key="PL000000019959">曹山</placeName>，參問之者堂<lb
ed="T" n="0786b26"/>盈室滿。其所詶對，<anchor xml:id="beg0786sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>邀</sic><corr>激</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0786sgsz7"/>射匪停，特為毳客標<lb
ed="T" n="0786b27"/>準，故排五位以銓量區域，無不盡其分<lb
ed="T" n="0786b28"/>齊也。復注《對<persName key="A004127">寒山子</persName>詩》，流行寓內，蓋以<persName key="A009449">寂</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0786b29"/>素修舉業之優也。文辭<anchor xml:id="beg0786004"/>遒<anchor xml:id="end0786004"/>麗，號富有法<pb ed="T" n="0786c" xml:id="T50.2061.0786c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0786c01"/>才焉。尋示疾，終于山，春秋六十二，<anchor xml:id="beg0786005"/>僧<anchor xml:id="end0786005"/>臘三<lb
ed="T" n="0786c02"/>十七。弟子奉龕窆而樹塔。後<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName><persName key="A010511">玄泰</persName>著<lb
ed="T" n="0786c03"/>塔銘云。</p>
